1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to crimes and offenses; to amend section
2 28-101, Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2024; to prohibit
3 interference with railroad infrastructure, equipment, and personnel
4 as prescribed; to define terms; to harmonize provisions; and to
5 repeal the original section.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
